snippet.title: Lean Simulator: Desperation - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Lean Simulator: Desperation is an upcoming Clicker Survival game with a Meme Horror tone that I've been developing.

How long can you survive?

You can wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2936620/Lean_Simulator_Desperation/

Songs Used:
1) "Interloper" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)

Licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 4.0 License
